lead_paragraph: The NBA says two calls were missed in the final moments of Cleveland's win over Golden State on Sunday, and both aided the Cavaliers in what became their one-point victory.

headline.print_headline: NBA: 2 Calls Were Missed in Final Moments of Cavs-Warriors
